Sharon, an agent of the local merchant’s guild, is sent to find out who is leaking guild secrets to the press. She manages to locate one of the journalists involved and narrates that she is going to pretend to be a great fan and attempt to get the journalist to reveal his source through flattery. The table decides that //Empathy// + //Persuasion// is a reasonable aptitude and skill for this attempt.
